Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.34,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,Japan lost the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.86,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,But humanity is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:49.38,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,I'm sure a city will be built over this burnt down field and it'll be bustling with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:58.09,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,I plan to make Japanese Empire Security Service a tractor for post-war reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:02.25,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,With it, I'll create businesses operated by both government and private enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:06.31,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,Eventually, this will lead to a global corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:10.56,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,That's my last job.  I'll dedicate the rest of my life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:15.03,Yaku T,Rur,0,0,0,,In other words, you won't support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:18.93,Yaku T,Man,0,0,0,,Ruriko-san, you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:21.41,Yaku T,Rur,0,0,0,,I'll hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:28.04,Yaku T,Rur,0,0,0,,I will hate you, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.55,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,You were right, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:45.81,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,The Japanese Empire Security Service is now a global company called JACES.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:51.52,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,But I haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:58.28,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,Please laugh at me for being a tenacious woman, Uncle Yakushiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.80,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Is my usual seat open?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.35,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,It practically is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.74,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,We are in the training region.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:54.24,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Is it true that if your house is in a designated training region, no one can stay there anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:55.15,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.15,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,It's really troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.07,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,So you've gone for a walk, Monami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.80,Yaku M,Tax,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.94,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak to you about Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.91,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Can we meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.52,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,What?  Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.58,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:01.18,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'd like to report the results from my investigation so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.29,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.05,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.57,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:10.95,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I heard rumors that you were sniffing around Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.16,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:18.20,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,If you're going to see Izumida, I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:22.84,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell me the content of your so-called investigation report too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:24.14,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.56,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's no use refusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.51,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'll find out once I torture Izumida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:36.02,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,The innocent Izumida-kun will end up suffering if you're stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.23,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,You're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:46.77,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Say, do you intend to stay quiet until we reach there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:51.12,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,I can tell you if you answer my question truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.91,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is that so?  In that case, ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.37,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,First, regarding this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.12,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Oh, Isurugi Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.45,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,What's with your reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:05.55,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Were you conducting your secret investigation without knowing her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.97,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.52,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.32,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Izumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.78,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.81,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,C-Could you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:34.21,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Monami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.43,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Oui, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.85,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.79,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Just the other day, you were still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.04,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.30,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Have you already discovered the links between Isurugi Ruriko and NPP?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:55.01,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,The Japan Private Police, the second largest security service company, splits the security industry market with JACES.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:58.98,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Ruriko is NPP's secret owner, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.77,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.77,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Right after the war, my grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:11.91,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yakushiji Masamoto and Isurugi Ruriko tried to make Japan's largest security service company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:16.06,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,But Ruriko was following a secret agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:22.39,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,The plan was to hire ex-soldiers from army and navy units that disbanded at the end of the war
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:26.21,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,and remilitarize Japan under the cloud of a security service.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.92,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.95,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:35.81,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,In fact, all the private security service employees in Iraq right now are ex-soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.05,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,That's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:45.95,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Anyway, my grandfather refused to support Ruriko and built a company alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:50.72,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,The Japanese Empire Security Service became the forerunner of JACES.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.03,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,And what about Isurugi Ruriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:57.60,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,After she disappeared for some time, she built NPP,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.06,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,but her original plan was never fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:06.29,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,And she hates the Yakushijis for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:11.47,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,In your case, there are many more who hate you besides her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.60,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.96,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.05,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.46,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.72,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:23.35,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,You said right after the war ended... how old does that make Ruriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.56,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I found this in the main house on Kamakura Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:30.42,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,There are no traces of the photograph being altered at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:36.95,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.30,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,I completely forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.70,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent Muromachi is headed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.08,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Monami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.14,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Izumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.26,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.30,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if someone sees us like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.17,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Th-That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.06,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.95,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Izumida, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.35,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent Muromachi, right now I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.03,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.88,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,No, that's not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.18,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.67,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Lieutenant Izumida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.60,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,This is a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.29,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.68,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,She looks identical to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.75,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:36.88,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,No, when I look carefully, she's a lot younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.51,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,You don't need to say anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.64,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Monami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:51.57,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,You've grown up a fair bit while you were away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.49,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Although it looks like my breasts are bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.66,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,You don't need to say anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.70,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.12,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.17,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.30,Yaku M,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oryo's relative or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.44,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,I don't know how I should explain this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:18.59,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Say, Monami, you should come to my place as originally planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.55,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.48,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:23.01,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.48,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,You're trying to take me somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:29.23,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.84,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,I'll stay with Izumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.98,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,I'm going to live here with Izumida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.36,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Izumida-kun, what are your thoughts on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.58,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Do you want to live here with Monami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:46.87,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Even if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.51,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Then how about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.65,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Monami.  Izumida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.73,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Both of you come to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.28,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:59.34,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'll stop talking about taking you out of the country too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:00.84,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.69,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.59,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,You still don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:09.06,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,In that case, do you want to pinky-swear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.37,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Izumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.82,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Say, "Ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:29.99,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Does it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.53,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.80,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.55,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Izumida, you're really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:41.22,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Since you can eat breakfast with a beautiful lady and a pretty girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.64,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Say, "Ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.48,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's from Marianne.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:49.48,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,When are those two coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.70,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,They were both in Paris, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.34,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:56.76,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I asked a perfumer I know to make me a perfume,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.74,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,but it looks like it'll take more time to complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:05.85,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's a list of people who have entered and left the Shiba government building in the last two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.41,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.54,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Did you notice something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.08,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,There are a few odd people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:22.81,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,They're all people from the medical field, a field that doesn't have any relation to Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.37,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,They're former executives of the Tsukuyomi Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.67,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,The Tsukuyomi Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:32.69,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,They were controlling human growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:37.73,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Ruriko probably used their research to make Monami grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:42.92,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,To begin with, what is Isurugi Ruriko like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.75,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I have to tell that story again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.45,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I just told the long story to Oyuki the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.90,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I didn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.25,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.20,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Izumida-kun, did you just laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.68,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,N-No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.30,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is that so?  Then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.77,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,This is just a secret between the two of us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:17.23,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Mistress Ryoko probably has feelings for Izumida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:24.92,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,To her, solving mysteries with Izumida-san is a time of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:32.04,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Just like how lovers talk about love, they go about solving supernatural crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.25,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,What about Izumida?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.97,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,What does he think about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:44.49,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Izumida-san has yet to notice her feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.51,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,But he should eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.14,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,And the two will be united.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.23,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.86,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,I now have a general understanding of who Isurugi Ruriko is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.36,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Now that leaves three mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:10.32,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,First is how Isurugi keeps her youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:15.74,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,The second is her relationship with Monami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:20.33,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,What is she planning to do with Monami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:23.40,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,The third is Monami-chan herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.67,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Who exactly is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.01,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,And the fourth mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.62,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.42,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Bear with it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.53,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,This is the only place they're not bugging.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:44.90,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Who exactly is the person who set up the bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.84,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Who do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:53.30,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Umm, since we're in this situation, please just tell me if you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:54.10,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.12,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.38,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.84,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's Nonagase-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.11,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:00.88,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:05.46,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Well, he's the only outsider who can enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.69,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:12.25,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Either he's just an enthusiast or he's a spy that Ruriko sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.60,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Either way, we need to identify him and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.27,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:21.23,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,J-Just... something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.07,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,So this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:34.05,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,You don't seem too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.72,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Is this regarding Izumida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.17,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,You can consult me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.74,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.88,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.34,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Let's go for a drive the next time we have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.44,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Look after the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.02,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.31,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,We'll probably be late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:00.23,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,You should go ahead and rest before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.95,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:25.88,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.63,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,There is someone I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.56,Yaku M,Mar,0,0,0,,That's the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.88,Yaku M,Sat,0,0,0,,Let's follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:45.69,Yaku M,Kuo,0,0,0,,But why did she tell us to follow her company's car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:49.90,Yaku M,Mar,0,0,0,,We won't be dragged into a strange case again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.50,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,Oh, keep a little more distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.49,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,Let an unrelated car come in between us from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.12,Yaku M,Mar,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.81,Yaku M,Sat,0,0,0,,Maruoka-san, you're really into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:01.80,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I followed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.40,Yaku M,Mar,0,0,0,,Should we let her know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.62,Yaku M,Sat,0,0,0,,I'll e-mail her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.64,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.39,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:17.86,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:33.90,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.11,Yaku M,Sat,0,0,0,,Ah!  She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.05,Yaku M,Mar,0,0,0,,They went inside here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:46.31,Yaku M,Old,0,0,0,,This is the only entrance, so I doubt they've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.37,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.25,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.66,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.98,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:52.07,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like our first meeting, even though it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:53.57,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,It's like I can tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.62,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,The man you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.95,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,...was it Izumida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.98,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:05.66,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,I'm interested in what he thinks of Ryoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:11.65,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,It's a defective product Ruriko-san made with great care,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:17.05,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,but unfortunately it did not bear a soul, and its body rotted while it was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.96,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,We call it the living dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:25.30,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Gather the bones of the dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:29.72,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,line them up in order from head to toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.48,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Apply medicine by the name of Hisou to the bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.48,Yaku Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,[Note: Hisou is Arsenic Trioxide.]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:36.19,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,After mixing with strawberry and chickweed leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:40.20,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,tie up the bones with strings from young Wisteria leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.83,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,and wash them thoroughly with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.75,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Where hair should exist on the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.62,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,apply ashes of Gleditsia and Hibiscus leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:56.06,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Lay tatami mats on dirt, and on them, lay the bones,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.09,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,and organize them before the wind breezes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.38,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,After 27 days have passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:04.70,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,go and burn aloes and incense,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.31,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,and conduct the secret art of Hangon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.31,Yaku Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,[Note: Hangon is the revitalization of the dead.]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.52,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,The secret art of Hangon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:14.45,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,The secret formula to create man from corpses.  It's said that Saigyou Houshi had performed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.27,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,As expected from Izumida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:21.14,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,You're as knowledgeable as Mistress Ryoko regarding things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:27.04,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,Ruriko-san is a descendant of a noble who taught the secret arts of Hangon to Saigyou Houshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:35.50,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,By mixing ancient, secret arts with modern cloning techniques, we can create anyone we wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.11,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.92,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.22,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,You were with her all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.79,Yaku M,Non,0,0,0,,With Ruriko-san's creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.52,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:51.94,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.04,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:21:01.82,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,If you take the place of the current Ryoko-san and become Yakushiji Ryoko, everything will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:05.78,Yaku M,Mon,0,0,0,,If I do, will Izumida then love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:09.12,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,I would think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.87,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,To shoot without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.43,Yaku M,Rur,0,0,0,,That's to be expected of you, Ryoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.97,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Now that I'm unarmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:42.65,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,whether it be grilling me or torturing me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:48.12,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,do whatever you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:17.87,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask this since we're on the topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:18.41,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:21.46,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Izumida-kun, you used to go out with a girlfriend whom you had the intention of marrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:23.00,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Yakushiji Ryoko's Supernatural Case File,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.94,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,File Number 09-D:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:27.17,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Tokyo.  Dead or Love.  Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:28.28,Yaku M,Jun,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:29.30,Yaku M,Ryo,0,0,0,,Say, is she...
